GoodForm

A CodeIgniter Libary for building forms

GoodForm is a CodeIgniter library for building GoodForms. The GoodForm library 
replaces existing form functionality provided by the CodeIgniter Form helper. 
GoodForm creates forms as objects, providing uniform methods to build your form 
programatically as well as flexiblity to customise your forms. The GoodForm 
object allows you to define labels, descriptions and field errors to create rich forms.